name: Unicorn Edition - Cross My Heart
description:
This is very unique necklace is part of my Unicorn Edition in which pieces will make rare appearances in limited quantities.

This necklace will definately grab alot of attention from onlookers! The heart shaped pendant features two arrows crossed in the center and finished with off with bright ruby red glitter contrast against a dark canvas, giving this piece a striking appearance!

The pendant measures 2 inches tall by 2 inches wide and hangs from a 24" gunmetal black ball chain necklace. Each pendant is handcrafted by me, therefore please allow slight variance per necklace.

name: Sweet Poison - Crossed Heart Candy Oval Necklace
description:

The pendant measures 1.25" tall by 1.5" wide and hangs from a 24" silver ball chain necklace. Each pendant is handcrafted by me, therefore please allow slight variance per necklace.

Please allow 5-7 days for production time.

name: Gear Up - Cogs and Gears Clockwork Necklace
description:
Introducing my Gear Up Collection for the avid clockwork and steampunk lover!

This steampunk inspired piece compliments any outfit . Embedded with cogs and gears on top a glitter background that gives this pendant a classy yet modern look. 

The pendant measures approx 1.25" tall by 1.5" wide and hangs from a 24" silver ball chain necklace. Each pendant is handcrafted by me, therefore please allow slight variance per necklace.

Please allow 5-7 days for production time.
